e and submits the delivery location modal.\n344:      * Waits for the modal to close after submission.\n345:      */\n346:     async setDeliveryPostalCode(postalCode: string): Promise<void> {\n347:         await this.postalCodeInput.fill(postalCode);\n348:         await this.updateDeliveryLocationButton.click();\n349:         // Modal closes programmatically; wait for it to be removed/hidden\n350:         await this.deliveryLocationModal.waitFor({ state: 'hidden', timeout: 10_000 }).catch(() => {\n351:             // Some renders close via CSS; fallback — just wait briefly\n352:         });\n353:     }\n354: \n355:     /**\n356:      * Adds the current product to the cart and waits for the \"View Cart & Checkout\"\n357:      * confirmation button to appear, which confirms a successful add.\n358:      */\n359:     async addToCart(): Promise<void> {\n360:         await this.addToCartButton.waitFor({ state: 'visible', timeout: 10_000 });\n361:         await this.addToCartButton.click();\n362:         await this.viewCartAndCheckoutButton.waitFor({ state: 'visible', timeout: 20_000 });\n363:     }\n364: }"}}
